tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"gold"},{"text":"Table requires 3 meter height space, and at least 1 meter of empty space is also required outward around the table. In versions before 1.21, the table model uses the old item-frame-based setup, which only supports the default ball radius and therefore uses textured cloths (cloth_rag_*.png). In 1.21 and later versions, if the ball radius is changed, or if the 1:2 playable-area adjustment is enforced, the table model will use the new item-display-based setup instead. This allows the table to be stretched or shrunk dynamically for different ball radii and table proportions. However, because stretching and shrinking textured cloths can cause overlapping visual glitches, the new setup only supports pure-color cloths, which use cloth_pure_*.png in the resource pack. If you want to create custom cloth textures, please keep this limitation in mind. You can adjust these behaviors using the settings under equipment."}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇ ","color":"gold"},{"text":"球桌需要三米高度空间，周围向外也需要至少一米的空间。在 1.21 之前的版本中，球桌模型使用旧的物品展示框方案，该方案只支持默认球半径，因此会使用带纹理的球桌布（cloth_rag_*.png）。 在 1.21 及之后版本中， 如果修改了球半径，或启用了 1:2 可击打区域调整， 球桌模型会改用新的物品展示实体方案。该方案可以根据不同球半径和球桌比例动态拉伸或缩放球桌模型。不过，由于带纹理的球桌布在拉伸或缩放后可能出现重叠相关的显示问题，新方案仅支持纯色球桌布，对应资源包中的 cloth_pure_*.png。 如果你想制作自己的球桌布， 请注意这一限制。相关行为可通过 equipment 下的设置进行调整。"}]
